staar investment trust/the
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Investment Management
The Staar Investment Trust is an investment advisor. The Company offers no-load mutual funds to IRAs, rollovers, 401(k), trusts, endowments, college education savings, and long-term investment accounts.




