Capital Markets

Company Overview of STAAR Investment Trust - STAAR Smaller Company Stock Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
STAAR Investment Trust - STAAR Smaller Company Stock Fund is an open ended fund of funds launched and managed by STAAR Financial Advisors, Inc. The fund invests in funds which invest in the public equity markets of the United States.  It invests in funds which invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in funds which invest in the value and growth stocks of small-cap, micro-cap, and mid-cap companies. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Russell 2000 Index. The fund was formerly known as STAAR System Trust - STARR Smaller Company Stock Fund. STAAR Investment Trust - STAAR Smaller Company Stock Fund was formed on April 4, 199...
STAAR Investment Trust - STAAR Smaller Company Stock Fund is an open ended fund of funds launched and managed by STAAR Financial Advisors, Inc. The fund invests in funds which invest in the public equity markets of the United States.  It invests in funds which invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in funds which invest in the value and growth stocks of small-cap, micro-cap, and mid-cap companies. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Russell 2000 Index. The fund was formerly known as STAAR System Trust - STARR Smaller Company Stock Fund. STAAR Investment Trust - STAAR Smaller Company Stock Fund was formed on April 4, 1996 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


